<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verify Your Email - CitadelBuy</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .header-icon { font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
    .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
    .header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin: 10px 0 0; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .message { color: #666; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .verification-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 30px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; border: 2px dashed #667eea; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; padding: 16px 40px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; margin: 20px 0; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4); }
    .cta-button:hover { opacity: 0.9; box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.6); }
    .divider { height: 1px; background: #e0e0e0; margin: 30px 0; }
    .alternative { background: #fff3cd; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; }
    .alternative h4 { margin: 0 0 10px; color: #856404; font-size: 16px; }
    .alternative p { margin: 0; color: #856404; font-size: 14px; }
    .alternative code { background: #fff; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 14px; color: #333; display: inline-block; margin-top: 10px; word-break: break-all; }
    .security-notice { background: #e3f2fd; border-radius: 6px; padding: 15px; margin: 25px 0; text-align: center; }
    .security-notice p { margin: 0; color: #1565c0; font-size: 14px; }
    .security-notice strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .info-box { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin: 20px 0; padding: 15px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 6px; }
    .info-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-right: 15px; }
    .info-text { flex: 1; font-size: 14px; color: #666; }
    .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
    .footer a { color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; }
    .footer-brand { font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .cta-button { padding: 14px 30px; font-size: 16px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="header-icon">&#128274;</div>
      <h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>
      <p>One quick step to get started</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="greeting">Hi {{name}},</div>

      <div class="message">
        <p>Welcome to CitadelBuy! To complete your registration and start enjoying all the benefits of your account, please verify your email address.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="verification-box">
        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; color: #666; font-size: 16px;">Click the button below to verify your email:</p>
        <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="cta-button">Verify Email Address</a>
        <p style="margin: 20px 0 0; color: #999; font-size: 13px;">This link will expire in {{expiryHours}} hours</p>
      </div>

      <div class="alternative">
        <h4>&#9888; Button not working?</h4>
        <p>Copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <code>{{verificationUrl}}</code>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <span class="info-icon">&#10004;&#65039;</span>
        <div class="info-text">
          <strong>Why verify your email?</strong><br>
          Email verification helps us ensure account security and allows you to receive important order updates, shipping notifications, and exclusive offers.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="security-notice">
        <p>
          <strong>&#128712; Security Notice</strong>
          If you didn't create an account on CitadelBuy, you can safely ignore this email or contact our support team.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="message" style="margin-top: 30px;">
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #999;">
          Need help? Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #667eea;">{{supportEmail}}</a> or visit our <a href="{{helpUrl}}" style="color: #667eea;">Help Center</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p class="footer-brand">CitadelBuy</p>
      <p>The Marketplace You Can Trust</p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-top: 15px;">
        &copy; {{currentYear}} CitadelBuy. All rights reserved.<br>
        <a href="{{privacyUrl}}">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="{{termsUrl}}">Terms of Service</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
